snippet.title: Remnant: From the Ashes - Swamps of Corsus - Survival Mode Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP1980-CUSA10507_00-REMNANT000000001

In Remnant: From the Ashes - Swamps of Corsus, prepare to face a new set of challenges in Survival Mode which will leave you with only a pistol and scrap - as you fight challenging bosses in search of upgraded loot across unique worlds. How far can you make it in one life? 

Coming soon to PlayStation 4.
